Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:07.359
Welcome to Ahmet's kitchen, today we will be making rice

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:10.079
Brown Rice 300g

00:00:10.079 --> 00:00:12.209
300g lamb meat

00:00:12.209 --> 00:00:13.959
2 onions

00:00:13.959 --> 00:00:15.899
Chili peppers

00:00:15.899 --> 00:00:18.979
Vegetable stock and chicken broth

00:00:18.979 --> 00:00:23.970
and dried vegetables

00:00:23.970 --> 00:00:24.570
lets start with the meat

00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:27.480
I have 50g margarine in the pot

00:00:29.590 --> 00:00:36.590
add meat

00:00:43.690 --> 00:00:50.690
fry

00:00:53.010 --> 00:01:00.010
after 5 minutes add onions

00:01:07.950 --> 00:01:10.680
again let it cook for 5 minutes

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.330
lets continue

00:01:15.580 --> 00:01:17.230
let it fry

00:01:27.530 --> 00:01:29.460
5 minutes are up

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:35.050
Now another chilli and tomato paste

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:37.020
stir

00:01:37.020 --> 00:01:38.570
until it gets color

00:01:45.730 --> 00:01:52.730
now you can see that it got the color

00:02:02.250 --> 00:02:09.250
Now the rice

00:02:13.359 --> 00:02:20.359
stir

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.099
add some vegetables

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:40.339
a spoonful of vegetable stock and chicken broth

00:02:47.119 --> 00:02:52.809
Pepper

00:02:52.809 --> 00:02:56.599
Salt

00:02:56.599 --> 00:03:01.019
water

00:03:02.809 --> 00:03:09.809
lets see what it looks like, stir

00:03:17.349 --> 00:03:18.519
done

00:03:21.779 --> 00:03:26.639
the water should be about 1cm higher than the rice

00:03:26.639 --> 00:03:29.979
cover

00:03:29.979 --> 00:03:32.149
let it cook slowly

00:03:32.149 --> 00:03:34.979
for about 20 minutes

00:03:34.979 --> 00:03:37.159
Then the rice is ready

00:03:37.159 --> 00:03:38.649
until next time, bye, Ahmet :)

